Subject: FSAC jobs fail - unable to start scan
Description: Stealthbits.StealthAUDIT.DataCollectors.FSAA.FSAAException: Unable to start scan: Proxy host list is either empty or no proxies were configured to scan the target host at Stealthbits.StealthAUDIT.DataCollectors.FSAA.ActivityScanTask.InternalProcessRecord() at Stealthbits.StealthAUDIT.DataCollectors.Tasks.Task.StartExecute()
Solution_Comment__c: Previously communication ports were blocked. Then, the credentials used for connection were not authorized to login to NetApp SVM. Finally, remote registry service was not enabled.
